  "title": "Sales Manager (Semiconductor MNC)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is one of the leading players in the Semiconductor sector. Due to business needs, they are now recruiting a Sales and Marketing Manager to be part of their Marketing team for ongoing transformation projects. They are located in the East – easily accessible.</strong></p>\n<p>Responsibilities of <strong>Sales and Marketing Manager</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Grow the business by developing new accounts and supporting existing customers.</li>\n  <li>Identify, engage, and convert sales opportunities with semiconductor assembly and test companies across Asia.</li>\n  <li>Plan and implement sales and marketing strategies to meet revenue goals and drive business expansion.</li>\n  <li>Establish and maintain strong relationships with key stakeholders and decision-makers.</li>\n  <li>Work closely with engineering and project teams to ensure equipment solutions meet customer needs.</li>\n  <li>Represent the company in client meetings, product demonstrations, and industry events or exhibitions.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma or Degree in engineering field</li>\n  <li>Min 3-5 years of sales and marketing experience in backend semiconductor industry</li>\n  <li>Good communication skills</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p>\n<p><strong>Email: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></p>\n<p>RecruitPedia Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 19C9682</p>\n<p>EA Personnel No: R2198636 (Oh Puey Xin)</p>",
